{"_path":"/zh/guide/introduction","_dir":"guide","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"介绍","description":null,"icon":"lucide:info","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"vue3-mobile-table"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 是一款专为 Vue 3 生态设计的轻量化、高性能的移动端表格引擎。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"它解决两大核心痛点："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"成熟的移动端表格组件匮乏"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"成熟的桌面端组件在移动端使用时体验糟糕"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通过极简的指令式接入，只需一行代码，即可赋予 Element Plus、Ant Design Vue 等任意 PC 端表格组件原生级的丝滑移动端交互体验。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"核心特性"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心特性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"物理仿真惯性引擎"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 采用基于 Delta Time 的帧率归一化技术，彻底消除不同屏幕刷新率带来的速度差异，在任意 HZ 屏幕下均能提供一致的丝滑体感。内置智能惯性保护：识别手指停顿意图，有效防止误触发惯性滑动。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"手势意图与方向轴锁定"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 毫秒级判定手势意图，自动过滤对角线抖动。在整个手势期间将操作锁定在单一轴向（横向或纵向），彻底解决长表格浏览过程中的「斜向漂移」痛点。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"智能边缘感知机制"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 自动探测滚动边界。当滚动触及尽头时，平滑地将事件控制权交还给浏览器，完美兼容 iOS 侧滑返回等系统级原生交互。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"动态急停点击保护"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 智能区分「刹车」与「触发」。仅在高速惯性滚动中拦截点击事件以实现即时避震，防止在翻阅数据时发生误触。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多指追踪与手势自适应"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 基于 Touch ID 锁定活跃指代，消除多指交替时的坐标跳变。检测到多指手势（如缩放）时，引擎自动进入静默模式，由浏览器接管原生行为。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主流 UI 库深度适配"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 内置 Element Plus、Ant Design Vue、Naive UI、VxeTable 等十余款主流组件库的预设配置，一行代码即可实现深度的交互优化。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多态设备自适应 (Lazy Hijacking)"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 针对 Surface/触屏笔记本等混合设备优化的状态机。纯鼠标操作零侵入，仅在触摸触发时按需唤醒，确保不同输入方式间的无缝切换。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"横屏场景手势校准"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 深度适配 CSS "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"transform: rotate()"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 场景。通过坐标轴智能映射自动修正触摸轨迹，确保横屏模式下的滑动方向与操作直觉完全一致，且无额外计算开销。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"轻量化零依赖"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 纯原生 TypeScript 实现，无任何第三方包依赖。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"解决了什么问题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"解决了什么问题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vue 生态中尚未出现可对标主流桌面表格栈的移动端 Table 方案。在报表等复杂业务场景下，移动端同样需要具备高性能与完整交互能力的表格组件，但当前生态存在明显空缺。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"实际落地通常只有两种路径：其一，自研表格组件，但触控交互、滚动机制与复杂功能实现成本极高，开发与维护负担沉重；其二，复用 Element Plus 等桌面端表格组件，但由于未针对移动端优化，在触控与小屏场景下普遍存在体验问题。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"复用桌面表格时，常见痛点包括："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对角线滑动误触"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 用户本想横向查看表格数据，却因手指路径不直而意外触发页面纵向滚动，导致视线丢失"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"滚动方向不纯粹"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 手指轻微倾斜就可能在横纵轴之间频繁切换，滑动路径显得杂乱"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"滚动不跟手"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 在复杂 UI 组件嵌套场景中，原生 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"overflow: auto"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 常出现明显滞后"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"缺少惯性反馈"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 松手后滚动立即中断或惯性生硬，远距离浏览需要反复拖拽"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"表头滚动撕裂"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 表体滚动时固定表头无法像素级同步，出现错位或延迟"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不同设备体感差异"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 刷新率差异导致同一套代码在不同设备上手感不一致"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"手势冲突"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 多指操作坐标跳变，或边界处干扰 iOS 侧滑返回等系统手势"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"混合设备干扰"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 在 Surface、触屏笔记本等设备上盲目劫持会影响鼠标与触控板使用"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CSS 旋转横屏坐标错乱"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"transform: rotate()"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 场景下触摸物理方向与逻辑滚动方向错位"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"v-mobile-table"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 通过接管触摸事件流，在指令内以滚动物理引擎应对上述问题；实现细节见 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/zh/how-it-works/how-it-works"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工作原理"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"工作原理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工作原理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"该指令通过接管触摸事件流，在内部实现方向判定、速度采样、惯性衰减、边缘交还与混合设备策略等完整滚动物理机制，保证移动端滚动既跟手又稳定。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你可以在 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/zh/how-it-works/how-it-works"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工作原理"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 中查看完整机制说明与关键实现思路。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"适用场景"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"适用场景"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"数据查看"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据查看"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"面向移动端的宽表、财务报表、对账清单等复杂数据展示场景。需要在有限屏幕内支持横向拖拽、纵向浏览、排序及嵌套表等多维交互，对表格功能、触控体验与渲染性能要求较高。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"跨端一致体验"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"跨端一致体验"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"同一业务页面需同时覆盖 PC 与移动端，在不重写表格业务逻辑的前提下，实现一致且可预期的交互体验。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"下一步"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下一步"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"跟随 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/zh/guide/configuration"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 从安装到高级选项完成配置"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value